    • Method Detail

      • create

        public T create(String name,
                Object... arguments)
        Creates a defined service implementation. The name can be either the fully-qualified class name or the simplified acronym. The acronym is the class name without package and service suffix.

        The acronym for org.tinylog.writers.RollingFileWriter is for example rolling file.

        Parameters:
        name - Acronym or class name of service implementation
        arguments - Arguments for constructor of service implementation
        Returns:
        A new instance of service or null if failed to create service

      • createAll

        public Collection<T> createAll(Object... arguments)
        Creates all registered service implementations.
        Parameters:
        arguments - Arguments for constructors of service implementations
        Returns:
        Instances of all service implementations
